profile:
The Home Improvement People have completed literally thousands of renovations since our inception. We are a unique award winning contracting company, consulted by various media as industry experts. 
Please view our website at homeimprovementpeople.com to view images of some of our projects. 
For our clients' convenience, we've implemented progress billing as well as financing.
Regardless of scope, we approach every single home renovation with a foundation of strong design aesthetics, comprehensive product options, sound project management, and a commitment to craftsmanship.
 
Our projects range from remodelled bathrooms and kitchens, to rear additions,  hardwood flooring, basements, second story additions and other extensive renovations. We undertake work in all budget ranges.
 
Choosing a reputable contractor is the most important decision you will make regarding your renovation. From plans and permits, to last little finishing details, The Home Improvement People is committed to completing your renovations and home improvements in a professional manner and to your complete satisfaction.
We take pride in our personalized service and our high quality workmanship. 
Call us for quality, insured work - completed on time, and on budget.
416-782-7605.

We specialize in designing homes, drafting the necessary construction drawings and then filing for the required building permits. 
This includes designing for new buildings, removal of a load-bearing wall, renovations, additions, garages, deck, basement conversions into suites and single-family home conversions into legal duplexes. 
We also provide client support and representation where a minor variance is required by the Committee of Adjustment. 
Do you have an upcoming construction project on your mind? 
Contact us today and we can offer you some helpful tips for getting started.

We are one of the most affordable places, which gives us the opportunity to provide you with an unbeatable quote keeping in mind the quality will stay intact of what you'll get in your place or better and we strongly believe that good relationships can maintain a healthy business.

Fine Finishes Design Inc. is a premier design and decorating firm serving the Greater Toronto area since 1997. 

We have a well earned reputation for attention to detail and professionalism in residential and commercial design.  Fine Finishes Design Inc. works closely with their clients and places special emphasis on understanding their unique needs, tastes and budget.  
Andrea Colman, the Principal Designer and Creative Director of Fine Finishes Design Inc. oversees each project personally ensuring the highest quality service.

Andrea graduated with the highest honours in the CIDC Design Program and is considered to be one of the best designers in the greater Toronto area.

Andrea is one of the founding members of The Benjamin Moore Painting and Decorating Services in North America and has sat on the Advisory Council for Benjamin Mooreâ€™s Painting and Decorating Services Canada.

Strong leadership and communication skills are the essential components necessary to navigate a construction project from concept to completion. Our extensive knowledge of all trade areas involved in both new construction and sophisticated renovations have proven invaluable to our company and our clients. Our recognition of the importance of scheduling cost control and quality control underlies and defines our successful completion of many challenging projects on time and within budget.

profile:
At Mignon Interiors, we Design, get your Permits and Approvals, and Build your Home.
Do you need a Full Home Renovation, New Construction, Extension, Addition, Second Floor, Basement or Kitchen Renovation?

We begin with a Free Consultation in your Home. We want to learn about your current layout, design and structural features. We also want to know what you do and don't like about your home. Next our Designer will do an extensive brainstorming of possible designs, colour tones and layouts. She will put together a proposal and recommend what styles go well with your home and preferences. The planning and design is the most important part of a home renovation. 

Next we have a Contractor with over 40 years of construction experience in Toronto. He will look at all the structural changes, interior and exterior finishes etc. to calculate your construction cost. We work with you and make adjustments until you are satisfied with the scope of your renovation and budget. Everything is on paper, we do not touch your home until you give us your approval. 

We then put together a rigid timeline and schedule. Materials are sourced and contractors begin their work. To keep your money safe, we want to minimize up front deposits and pay progress payments only after each stage is completed. Our goal is to keep you informed throughout the entire process, whilst allowing you to focus on your daily work, family and social life.

Welcome to Mignon Interiors, where we stand by our reputation. We are dedicated to giving you a positive experience and make sure you will be thrilled with your Brand New Home.

"My Prestigious Home" is where you need to be...

MPH has been a leader in major renovations and custom home construction since 2007. From concept to completion, we take a clientâ€™s vision and make it a reality through a comprehensive process to ensure the finished product exceeds expectations. So whether it be a new architecturally designed or inspired home, or a renovation and extension of your existing home, you can be guaranteed that MPH is most definitely the qualified team for your project.

We have had the opportunity to transform your dreams into reality by designing rooms where you can relax and your children can safely play. profile:
DSBG came to life based on the aspirations of professionals working in the construction industry that sought to create a truly different kind on construction services firm. We are committed to providing unparalleled customer service, the finest quality workmanship and a management team that attracts the best craftsmen and trades in the industry.

From our humble beginnings as Design-Spec Building Group Ltd., as renovators focused exclusively on residential renovations and new construction, we have consistently grown to become a full service general contracting and project management firm with unique expertise in both residential and commercial construction projects. We consistently invest in our greatest assets; our people, our management systems and our trades to ensure we remain the benchmark for excellence in residential and commercial construction.

Our management team has in excess of 80 years of combined construction and related management experience with relevant site expertise. Nick Malfara, President, has over 20 years of sales, project and business management experience in construction and related fields working for both local and large multi-national corporations. Mr. Malfara oversees all company operations and works closely in tandem with our Project Managers, Coordinators and Estimators to ensure that all commitments to our valued clients are met both on time and on budget.
Visit or call today to book your in-home consultation

We build beautiful modern homes of all shapes and sizes.
From heritage properties, condominiums, to new builds, we love reinventing and transforming contemporary spaces for design enthusiasts. We provide both design and construction services catered to our clientâ€™s needs. From ideation to filling your space with everything it needs, we provide a seamless full service to our clients.

HIGH QUALITY CRAFTMANSHIP
Contemporary is clean and simple. We have a passion for refinement of materiality and detailing. That is why we work with an extensive network of professionals who exceed expectations instead of managing them.

PROJECT MANAGEMENT
We believe in creating positive attitudes with our project team members and our clients. When weâ€™re excited about your project, it inspires others to be excited about it as well.

MODERN DESIGN

WE LOVE TO BUILD
Archetype Construction has over 20 years experience in the construction and design industry. profile:
BROOKVIEW FINE DECKS 

BUILD YOUR DREAM DECK OR BRING YOUR OLD WEATHERED DECK BACK TO LIFE! 

With over 20 years of Custom Deck Building experience, we offer a free comprehensive deck assessment whether building from scratch or restoring your weather beaten deck. 

We supply new deck quotes with custom drawings and the ability to change dimensions when required. 

We also offer deck repair and refinishing for those of you that just want to bring your deck back to it's original finish. A complete pressure washing with an environmentally friendly cleaning agent is applied and all dirt, grime, stain and mildew is removed. A light sanding to prepare the wood to accept the stain follows. After that, you are free to pick the color of your choice. All of this can be done in approximately 2 - 4 days. We will work within your schedule. 

Need a fence, gazebo or pergola built or restored? We will accommodate. 

CALL NOW FOR A FREE ESTIMATE! 
Office: 647-922-1853 

We service Toronto, Scarborough, Brampton, Etobicoke, Oshawa, Whitby, Ajax, Pickering, Mississauga, Vaughan, Richmond Hill, Thornhill, King City, Markham, Aurora and Newmarket. 

Office Hours: 
Monday: 7am - 9pm 
Tuesday: 7am - 9pm 
Wednesday: 7am - 9pm 
Thursday: 7am - 9pm 
Friday: 7am - 9pm 
Saturday: 9am - 5pm 
Sunday: 9am - 5pm 

Estimates within 1 hour outside our service area will be billed $50.
name: Brookview Fine Decks

3D surfaces are  craftsman decorative embossed slabs made with gypsum and additives used to transform rooms and spaces with three-dimensional visual and tactile effect.The environments are completely modified with 3D surfaces without having to undergo long renovations. In addition, the surfaces can be painted and adapted according to what the project requires, has a light sound absorption, it is easy to clean and has several models and shapes.

The team here at I P A N E M A design I build, we will do our very best to incorporate all of your needs into the perfect remodeling design. We have fine-tuned a step by step process that will make it seem easy. Your finished remodelling project is custom tailored to fit your needs while we focus on every detail from start to finish. 

The constant desire to research new ideas and personalize each project makes I P A N E M A design l build a unique entity in this sector. We also develop the most diverse types of design solutions to complete remodels following the desire and directions of each client with technology and high standard.

Our company is a full-service design company that provides comprehensive services in:

3D surfaces

profile:
Digital Design, Millwork & Fabrication
We help take your projects all the way from ideation to realization.
Whether you are a designer, a contractor, a person with an idea or a person with a space that needs a fit-out, millwork or piece of furniture, we will work with you every step of the way. 

We have two 5' x 10' (1524mm x 3048mm) 3 axis CNC router machines with a 10" Z-axis capability and more than seven years of experience offering CNC cutting services across Toronto, Canada and the United States. In this time we have realized numerous projects that were initially considered only possible with a 5 axis machine in sizes far beyond our machining area by various means we have become experienced with.

We offer high quality CNC cutting services, design, documentation, project management, interior design and millwork packages, prototyping, jigs and templating, assembly, finishing and installation. We are a turnkey solution.

profile:
Frontier Renovations & Design has been in business for 15(+) yrs and has been serving the GTA with quality renovations surpassing the average industry expectations. Our 25(+) yrs of experience offers our clients exceptional installation methods geared toward the diverse needs that are typical in the renovations industry. We have worked primarily on homes 60 years or older giving us the experience that is needed to successfully complete projects. We offer complete design/ build services for our clients.
 
Frontier Renovations & Design has had the great honor and privilege to employ our services on three hit TV shows for HGTV.
"INCOME PROPERTY" Seasons 4, 5 & 6- a show which offers homeowners the opportunity to have qualified Building Renovators to turn their single family dwelling into legal dual dwellings for the purpose of creating a passive income from their property, for 2-1/2 wonderfully successful seasons. 
New Projects
"Home to Win"- twenty two top HGTV designers and contractors design and renovate a dream home to be won by one of three lucky challengers in a battle royale: testing the creative and building practices of each team.
"$ave My Reno" Seasons 2, 3, & 4- homeowners reach out to Sebastian Clovis and Sabrina Smelko to help them with their home renovation that is on a strict budget. The homeowners invest sweat equity through assisting Sebastian and Sabrina with design, construction and Special Projects and custom builds.
name: Frontier Renovations & Design
